English Translation: The Holy Rosary 

The Holy Rosary is a Catholic prayer highly recommended to invoke the intercession of the Blessed Virgin Mary. Rooted in Scripture, sometimes called "the Gospel in miniature", its simplicity makes it ideal for private meditation, community prayer, and for family devotions. In this presentation, the traditional Catholic music, serves as a backdrop for the recitation of the Rosary, creating an inspiring environment in which anyone can easily pray.
